                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p>ally if it is printed in German and English, but at the same time. But,<lb/> in any\n                event, I must have the manuscript back. Please indicate to me<lb/> what you do not\n                understand or cannot read. In case you cannot include<lb/> in the\n                    <date>December</date> issue I must have the manuscript back, but you can<lb/>\n                print the German in English characters.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">If only I could get well and raise my spirits.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With heartfelt respect,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Sincerely yours,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Jonah Bondi</persName>\n            </p>\n            <pb n=\"Card\"/>\n            <p>„I<add>?</add>s jüd. Volk ist im symbolisher<add>?</add><lb/> R<add>?</add>g\n                    <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <persName>Chateaubriand</persName>, G<add>?</add><lb/> 5 <add>?</add>, 1. Capitel.\n                    (<add>?</add> bin Salvador<lb/> Rö<add>?</add>)</p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philad</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Pens.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>1227. Walnut Str.</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3445j45b/canvas/p2"
